  "body": "<p>Yet another fantastic month of kits at Studio Calico! I so enjoyed playing with the <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/front-row-scrapbook-kit?aff=6cc2c70f\">main kit</a> in addition to the <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/junior-mints?aff=6cc2c70f\">Junior Mints</a>, <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/matinee?aff=6cc2c70f\">Matinee</a>, and <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/big-screen?aff=6cc2c70f\">Big Screen</a> add-ons.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"23a-34-445x600.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600229792740-D1KBU4S0JO5N48OEJM0V/23a-34-445x600.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"23c-getaway-560x600.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600229770538-XJG5OWFC6STTNEJBC5R7/23c-getaway-560x600.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"23b-bamboo-564x600.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600229770533-6051Q00471LGMU6RT3VD/23b-bamboo-564x600.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"23d-hotlanta-561x600.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600229771125-EV4LBMXXTU7M7VCUTQ6Y/23d-hotlanta-561x600.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"23e-maui-562x600.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600229771153-YXDZTC7ZCNXVBAQV0S3A/23e-maui-562x600.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"23f-no_wonder-435x600.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600229771919-DZQ8L5658ZSGNWD2S365/23f-no_wonder-435x600.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"23g-.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600229771923-RIXCAJ9BX29H05GNCT34/23g-.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"23h-recently-562x600.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600229772339-FA4KZ0ODF9BJ5SB8NI6N/23h-recently-562x600.jpg\"/>"
